															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ihp" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1267048); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1267048&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610183102" alt="Ihp" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1267048)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ihp" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1267048); return false;" >Ihp</a></span> <span class="odate time_1404172936 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">01 Jul 2014 00:02</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2061248">
									

<p>This was originally started out as something simple: just Robert Bumaro giving a sermon to adherents of his church, professing acceptance for the splinter churches. It eventually evolved into him actually meeting members of the other two churches, and&#8230; well, this happened.</p>
<p>There is a bit of an easter egg in this story, and I won't say what it is, but suffice to say, if you've read up to a certain point of a certain story arc on the site, something in this story will seem very familiar to you.</p>

